descriptions.direction: Located in Omadhoo, Nemo Inn is on the beach. Villingilivaru Island Pier and Dhangethi Port are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Ari Atoll and Dhigurah Beach. Spend some time exploring the area's activities, including whale-watching.
descriptions.general: Offering a garden, Nemo Inn provides accommodations in Omadhoo. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk, and full-day security, along with free Wifi throughout the property. There's free private parking, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service. The guest house features some units with sea views, and units come with a private bathroom. At the guest house, some units are soundproof. There is a coffee shop and lounge. The area is popular for walking tours, and bike rental is available at this 3-star guest house. Outdoor play equipment is also available at the guest house, while guests can also relax on the sun terrace.
